1
00:02:08,590 --> 00:02:09,850
Tai Xuan Acupuncture?

2
00:02:09,910 --> 00:02:11,710
It really is the Tai Xuan Acupuncture.

3
00:02:11,710 --> 00:02:14,080
I saw it recorded
in an ancient medical text.

4
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:15,630
I thought it had been lost long ago.

5
00:02:15,630 --> 00:02:18,280
Never did I imagine it would
still be preserved among the people.

6
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:19,680
After a lifetime devoted to medicine,

7
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:21,960
to behold
the Tai Xuan Acupuncture once more—

8
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:23,710
I would die with no regrets.

9
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:08,520
I see.

10
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:10,520
The Tai Xuan Acupuncture

11
00:03:10,520 --> 00:03:11,590
is really amazing.

12
00:03:12,680 --> 00:03:13,630
Physician Chen.

13
00:03:13,630 --> 00:03:14,680
To be honest,

14
00:03:15,030 --> 00:03:17,800
what I used just now was indeed
the Tai Xuan Acupuncture.

15
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:19,310
Regrettably, my skills are limited—

16
00:03:19,310 --> 00:03:21,040
I have only learned its basics.

17
00:03:21,190 --> 00:03:23,079
Whether General Xiao
will survive the night unharmed

18
00:03:23,079 --> 00:03:24,520
remains to be seen.

19
00:03:24,520 --> 00:03:26,280
Physician Han, you are too modest.

20
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:27,240
Physician Chen.

21
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:29,520
The root of this illness is poison,

22
00:03:29,520 --> 00:03:30,910
and it's not contagious.

23
00:03:30,910 --> 00:03:33,079
We were helpless
because our treatment methods

24
00:03:33,079 --> 00:03:35,010
had been misguided from the start.

25
00:03:35,520 --> 00:03:36,360
Look.

26
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:38,680
The blood has congealed into powder.

27
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:39,310
Far from smelling foul,

28
00:03:39,310 --> 00:03:41,170
it carries an unusual fragrance.

29
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:43,400
Right.

30
00:03:44,280 --> 00:03:45,240
You mean that

31
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:46,360
General Xiao took the medicine

32
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:47,710
as a way of fighting poison with poison,

33
00:03:47,710 --> 00:03:48,910
but the toxin
remained trapped in his body.

34
00:03:48,910 --> 00:03:50,910
Only with the aid of acupuncture
can the poison be expelled.

35
00:03:50,910 --> 00:03:52,520
This use of acupuncture
to expel the toxin

36
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:54,380
was merely a fortunate accident.

37
00:03:55,079 --> 00:03:57,680
Today, I have truly witnessed
something extraordinary.

38
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:58,520
Physician Han.

39
00:03:58,520 --> 00:04:00,310
You are a talent of your generation,

40
00:04:00,310 --> 00:04:01,970
worthy of the highest praise.

41
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:03,680
You flatter me, Physician Chen.

42
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:05,630
Now that the medicine
has proven successful,

43
00:04:05,630 --> 00:04:07,870
I must hurry to
prepare it for the villagers

44
00:04:07,870 --> 00:04:09,630
and let everyone know the good news.

45
00:04:09,630 --> 00:04:10,840
As for General Xiao,

46
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:13,430
please stay here
for another night, Physician Chen.

47
00:04:13,430 --> 00:04:14,240
Okay.

48
00:04:14,680 --> 00:04:15,840
You brought General Xiao

49
00:04:15,840 --> 00:04:17,630
back from the verge of death.

50
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:19,040
I'm confident

51
00:04:19,040 --> 00:04:20,480
I can ensure his safety.

52
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:21,410
In that case,

53
00:04:21,680 --> 00:04:22,390
thank you.

54
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:41,480
General Xiao.

55
00:04:41,680 --> 00:04:42,600
You're awake.

56
00:04:43,430 --> 00:04:44,510
Looks like

57
00:04:44,510 --> 00:04:46,240
death didn't take me this time.

58
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:47,270
It was Physician Han

59
00:04:47,270 --> 00:04:49,000
who brought you back.

60
00:04:51,120 --> 00:04:51,950
Where is Yunling?

61
00:04:51,950 --> 00:04:53,240
Where is she?

62
00:04:53,310 --> 00:04:54,110
General Xiao.

63
00:04:54,310 --> 00:04:56,680
Risking your own life to test the medicine
was a righteous act.

64
00:04:56,680 --> 00:04:58,270
Physician Han spent the whole night
preparing the remedy

65
00:04:58,270 --> 00:04:59,510
for the patients—

66
00:04:59,510 --> 00:05:00,480
she probably

67
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:01,800
hasn't rested yet.

68
00:05:02,120 --> 00:05:03,050
I'll go find her.

69
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:12,480
When will they come out?

70
00:05:13,310 --> 00:05:15,190
Why aren't they out yet?

71
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:19,310
They're out. They're out.

72
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:25,800
They're out.

73
00:05:57,800 --> 00:05:59,190
My fellow villagers.

74
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:00,480
Everyone.

75
00:06:01,070 --> 00:06:02,040
We should all

76
00:06:02,040 --> 00:06:04,840
be grateful
to Physician Han for saving our lives.

77
00:06:05,430 --> 00:06:07,720
Thank you for saving our lives.

78
00:06:08,190 --> 00:06:10,310
Thank you for saving our lives.

79
00:06:10,310 --> 00:06:11,120
Everyone,

80
00:06:11,360 --> 00:06:12,800
you can go home.

81
00:06:13,430 --> 00:06:17,240
Let's go home.

82
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:18,750
Physician Han.

83
00:06:18,750 --> 00:06:19,950
We're going home too.

84
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:20,560
Okay.

85
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:21,780
Physician Han.

86
00:06:21,870 --> 00:06:23,040
Now that the patients have recovered,

87
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:24,630
we shall return to the capital.

88
00:06:24,630 --> 00:06:25,270
Farewell.

89
00:06:51,270 --> 00:06:52,400
You've worked hard.

90
00:06:55,390 --> 00:06:56,720
It's all over now.

91
00:07:09,510 --> 00:07:11,680
If you had listened to me

92
00:07:11,870 --> 00:07:14,240
and eliminated
the infected villagers then and there,

93
00:07:14,240 --> 00:07:16,800
none of this would have happened.

94
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:17,600
Lord Li.

95
00:07:18,480 --> 00:07:20,340
You don't agree with that, do you?

96
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:21,920
Your Majesty.

97
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:24,920
I think Lord Zhang is right.

98
00:07:25,270 --> 00:07:26,720
After all, the plague

99
00:07:26,720 --> 00:07:29,000
that struck
the people of Jinglan years ago

100
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:32,070
is still vivid in my mind.

101
00:07:32,070 --> 00:07:33,270
It was

102
00:07:33,270 --> 00:07:34,390
a terrible sight.

103
00:07:34,390 --> 00:07:37,270
Even now, the thought of it
fills me with fear.

104
00:07:37,390 --> 00:07:38,390
Your Majesty.

105
00:07:39,240 --> 00:07:42,190
I think what Lord Li said makes sense.

106
00:07:42,190 --> 00:07:44,510
Your Majesty, though you are merciful,

107
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:47,000
in matters of such great importance,

108
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:49,480
there must be no room for error.

109
00:07:49,870 --> 00:07:50,830
Otherwise,

110
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:52,360
your wise rule

111
00:07:52,360 --> 00:07:54,390
and the entire land of Jinglan

112
00:07:54,720 --> 00:07:57,240
will be brought to ruin.

113
00:07:57,240 --> 00:07:57,830
Right.

114
00:07:57,830 --> 00:07:58,720
Your Majesty.

115
00:07:59,870 --> 00:08:00,600
Lord Fei.

116
00:08:01,270 --> 00:08:02,270
What do you think?

117
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:04,600
I think

118
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:07,190
both lords have a point.

119
00:08:08,120 --> 00:08:09,600
But I still hold that

120
00:08:10,190 --> 00:08:11,600
as our ancestors taught us,

121
00:08:11,600 --> 00:08:14,200
among all under Heaven,
the people come first.

122
00:08:14,510 --> 00:08:16,630
Though Huangpi Village
is but a small place,

123
00:08:16,630 --> 00:08:18,390
the villagers remain His Majesty's people.

124
00:08:18,390 --> 00:08:20,270
Even in the time of the late Emperor,

125
00:08:20,270 --> 00:08:22,040
when the plague was at its worst,

126
00:08:22,040 --> 00:08:23,160
we never

127
00:08:23,160 --> 00:08:25,120
give up any citizen.

128
00:08:25,870 --> 00:08:27,120
Well said.

129
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:29,270
I am a wise ruler.

130
00:08:30,390 --> 00:08:32,480
As long as it is not the very last resort,

131
00:08:32,480 --> 00:08:35,270
I won't give up on anyone in Jinglan.

132
00:08:35,510 --> 00:08:37,630
There's news from Xiao Chi.

133
00:08:37,909 --> 00:08:38,960
Now,

134
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:40,870
Huangpi Village is under control.

135
00:08:40,870 --> 00:08:41,720
Lord Fei.

136
00:08:42,030 --> 00:08:44,750
Do not lie before His Majesty,

137
00:08:45,240 --> 00:08:46,080
or you will

138
00:08:46,270 --> 00:08:48,510
be punished for deceiving the Emperor.

139
00:08:48,670 --> 00:08:49,360
Lord Zhang.

140
00:08:49,840 --> 00:08:51,360
If I have spoken falsely,

141
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:52,820
I will accept punishment.

142
00:08:55,480 --> 00:08:56,440
Your Majesty,

143
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:57,510
a report from the front—

144
00:08:57,510 --> 00:08:59,030
Huangpi Village has been
freed of the plague,

145
00:08:59,030 --> 00:09:00,560
and all villagers are safe.

146
00:09:01,870 --> 00:09:02,670
Good.

147
00:09:03,270 --> 00:09:04,960
Heaven has indeed blessed Jinglan.

148
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:06,000
Xiao Chi

149
00:09:06,320 --> 00:09:07,720
is worthy of great merit.

150
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:09,040
Fei Zheng.

151
00:09:09,120 --> 00:09:09,910
Yes, Your Majesty.

152
00:09:09,910 --> 00:09:11,240
Go to Huangpi Village

153
00:09:11,630 --> 00:09:13,560
and bring General Xiao back for me.

154
00:09:13,630 --> 00:09:15,510
I'll personally reward him.

155
00:09:16,480 --> 00:09:17,000
Yes.

156
00:09:17,390 --> 00:09:18,190
Your Majesty.

157
00:09:18,480 --> 00:09:19,600
Lord Zhang.

158
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:20,670
Yes.

159
00:09:20,960 --> 00:09:22,360
Please go there

160
00:09:22,360 --> 00:09:24,080
and escort

161
00:09:24,510 --> 00:09:25,630
General Xiao back

162
00:09:26,150 --> 00:09:27,600
for me.

163
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:30,750
Yes.

164
00:09:31,150 --> 00:09:32,320
Your Majesty.

165
00:09:35,200 --> 00:09:37,720
Come on. Pour the wine.

166
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:38,510
Fill it up.

167
00:09:38,630 --> 00:09:40,270
Fill it up.

168
00:09:40,320 --> 00:09:41,120
Here you go.

169
00:09:41,120 --> 00:09:41,960
Physician Han.

170
00:09:41,960 --> 00:09:42,760
General Xiao.

171
00:09:43,510 --> 00:09:44,870
Without your help,

172
00:09:45,030 --> 00:09:46,270
Huangpi Village would never

173
00:09:46,270 --> 00:09:48,630
have overcome the Death Plague.

174
00:09:48,870 --> 00:09:50,440
On behalf of the villagers,

175
00:09:50,440 --> 00:09:51,600
I thank you both.

176
00:09:52,270 --> 00:09:54,240
Please accept this bow.

177
00:09:55,720 --> 00:09:58,270
Please accept our bow of gratitude.

178
00:10:03,870 --> 00:10:05,200
Please get up.

179
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:06,510
Get up.

180
00:10:08,030 --> 00:10:10,000
It's my duty.

181
00:10:10,080 --> 00:10:10,840
This is the result

182
00:10:10,840 --> 00:10:12,270
of everyone's effort.

183
00:10:12,480 --> 00:10:14,120
Chief, there is no need for such courtesy.

184
00:10:14,120 --> 00:10:15,030
Please get up.

185
00:10:15,720 --> 00:10:16,720
Please get up.

186
00:10:16,840 --> 00:10:17,720
Get up.

187
00:10:20,390 --> 00:10:21,240
Everyone,

188
00:10:21,870 --> 00:10:23,270
let's toast General Xiao

189
00:10:23,270 --> 00:10:24,720
and Physician Han.

190
00:10:24,720 --> 00:10:26,480
To General Xiao.

191
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:28,200
To Physician Han.

192
00:10:47,030 --> 00:10:47,840
Xiao Chi.

193
00:10:50,120 --> 00:10:52,180
I will definitely cure your illness.

194
00:11:01,240 --> 00:11:03,370
It's alright even if it can't be cured.

195
00:11:04,270 --> 00:11:06,510
Don't you want to live well?

196
00:11:10,200 --> 00:11:11,080
I do.

197
00:11:13,080 --> 00:11:13,910
Of course I do.

198
00:11:14,840 --> 00:11:15,720
But I'm afraid

199
00:11:15,910 --> 00:11:18,640
in the end, it will all be
nothing but an illusion.

200
00:11:20,720 --> 00:11:23,000
We have to look at the bright side.

201
00:11:24,510 --> 00:11:26,240
Though this illusion is unreal,

202
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:28,170
it once illuminated the darkness.

203
00:11:29,600 --> 00:11:31,120
Just like life itself—

204
00:11:31,120 --> 00:11:32,480
though filled with hardships,

205
00:11:32,480 --> 00:11:34,120
there is always a ray of light

206
00:11:34,270 --> 00:11:35,400
that shines upon us.

207
00:11:37,840 --> 00:11:38,630
Yes.

208
00:11:39,670 --> 00:11:40,840
In every heart,

209
00:11:41,960 --> 00:11:44,120
there is a warm light of its own.

210
00:11:55,240 --> 00:11:56,550
General, Physician Han.

211
00:11:56,550 --> 00:11:57,270
Zheng.

212
00:11:59,600 --> 00:12:01,460
You two seem to be in good spirits.

213
00:12:01,510 --> 00:12:03,240
However, even the best of moods

214
00:12:03,320 --> 00:12:05,580
cannot allow you to stay here any longer.

215
00:12:05,600 --> 00:12:06,630
Chu has ordered me

216
00:12:06,630 --> 00:12:07,890
to bring you both back.

217
00:12:08,120 --> 00:12:09,000
We can talk

218
00:12:09,200 --> 00:12:10,860
once we return to the capital.

219
00:12:11,510 --> 00:12:12,320
Okay.

220
00:12:20,390 --> 00:12:21,320
Your Highness.

221
00:12:21,670 --> 00:12:24,200
His Majesty went to
the Xiao Residence again.

222
00:12:27,720 --> 00:12:29,840
I would like to see

223
00:12:30,910 --> 00:12:32,710
the one he is so concerned about.

224
00:12:38,790 --> 00:12:40,120
That hairpin is pretty.

225
00:12:40,240 --> 00:12:40,910
Jin Xi.

226
00:12:40,910 --> 00:12:42,200
It suits you well.

227
00:12:46,670 --> 00:12:48,240
As your female official,

228
00:12:48,510 --> 00:12:51,080
I am not allowed
to wear any extra accessories.

229
00:12:51,080 --> 00:12:53,080
I don't even mind, so why should you?

230
00:12:53,240 --> 00:12:54,910
Jin Xi, get me an eyebrow brush.

231
00:12:54,910 --> 00:12:55,480
Okay.

232
00:12:56,120 --> 00:12:58,320
The Eldest Princess has arrived!

233
00:13:02,910 --> 00:13:04,240
Who are you?

234
00:13:04,240 --> 00:13:06,390
The Eldest Princess of
Jinglan has arrived.

235
00:13:06,390 --> 00:13:08,600
Have your princess kneel to pay respects.

236
00:13:08,600 --> 00:13:09,930
Liu Chu's elder sister?

237
00:13:16,240 --> 00:13:17,440
You may leave now.

238
00:13:18,270 --> 00:13:20,720
I want to talk to the Princess of Changmo.

239
00:13:35,240 --> 00:13:36,000
Look at you.

240
00:13:36,360 --> 00:13:37,080
Get up.

241
00:13:39,440 --> 00:13:41,000
We'll be a family soon.

242
00:13:41,000 --> 00:13:43,130
There's no need for such formalities.

243
00:13:43,240 --> 00:13:44,510
You are

244
00:13:44,790 --> 00:13:45,720
so beautiful.

245
00:13:46,670 --> 00:13:49,130
Princess of Changmo,
you truly are a beauty.

246
00:13:49,840 --> 00:13:51,080
Thank you, Your Highness.

247
00:13:51,080 --> 00:13:52,360
You can call me Wanyu.

248
00:13:53,440 --> 00:13:54,000
Okay.

249
00:13:54,480 --> 00:13:55,240
Wanyu.

250
00:13:58,120 --> 00:13:59,960
What brings you here today?

251
00:14:00,510 --> 00:14:02,080
Liu Chu didn't send me.

252
00:14:02,270 --> 00:14:03,910
I came on my own to see you.

253
00:14:04,630 --> 00:14:06,600
Is Liu Chu busy?

254
00:14:08,480 --> 00:14:09,480
I mean,

255
00:14:09,750 --> 00:14:11,750
I've been in the capital for so long,

256
00:14:11,790 --> 00:14:13,440
and he has never summoned me.

257
00:14:13,790 --> 00:14:14,960
I don't even know

258
00:14:14,960 --> 00:14:16,910
when the marriage ceremony will be held.

259
00:14:16,910 --> 00:14:19,910
You haven't seen him
since you arrived in the capital?

260
00:14:23,910 --> 00:14:24,750
He has

261
00:14:24,840 --> 00:14:26,390
long been busy with court affairs.

262
00:14:26,390 --> 00:14:28,320
Even I find it difficult to see him.

263
00:14:28,910 --> 00:14:29,960
But I believe

264
00:14:30,360 --> 00:14:32,440
he won't keep you here for too long.

265
00:14:33,790 --> 00:14:34,600
That's good.

266
00:14:35,720 --> 00:14:37,520
Liu Chu has always called me Xie.

267
00:14:37,870 --> 00:14:40,870
Although the marriage ceremony
hasn't been held yet,

268
00:14:41,270 --> 00:14:42,600
I like you.

269
00:14:42,910 --> 00:14:44,270
You can also call me Xie.

270
00:14:45,790 --> 00:14:46,550
Xie.

271
00:14:52,080 --> 00:14:52,750
Xie.

272
00:14:53,000 --> 00:14:55,600
Is Liu Chu as good-looking as you?

273
00:14:57,240 --> 00:14:58,240
We are born

274
00:14:58,240 --> 00:14:59,630
of the same mother.

275
00:15:00,320 --> 00:15:01,790
Not only do we look alike,

276
00:15:02,240 --> 00:15:04,000
even our personalities

277
00:15:04,360 --> 00:15:05,510
are the same.

278
00:15:06,910 --> 00:15:07,720
That's good.

279
00:15:08,080 --> 00:15:10,940
I was worried Liu Chu
might be a very serious person.

280
00:15:11,600 --> 00:15:12,390
Xie.

281
00:15:12,720 --> 00:15:14,360
What does Liu Chu like?

282
00:15:15,200 --> 00:15:16,200
He...

283
00:15:18,390 --> 00:15:20,080
He will like you very much.

284
00:15:29,840 --> 00:15:31,640
What do you think of the capital?

285
00:15:31,720 --> 00:15:32,790
The city walls

286
00:15:32,790 --> 00:15:34,200
are tall and imposing,

287
00:15:34,480 --> 00:15:35,940
the streets are bustling,

288
00:15:37,240 --> 00:15:39,040
and there is plenty of good food.

289
00:15:40,030 --> 00:15:40,910
What else?

290
00:15:41,870 --> 00:15:44,120
I haven't been to other places yet.

291
00:15:44,720 --> 00:15:45,870
When you enter the palace,

292
00:15:45,870 --> 00:15:47,600
I'll take you around properly.

293
00:15:48,200 --> 00:15:49,080
Thank you, Xie.

294
00:15:50,270 --> 00:15:50,960
Xie.

295
00:15:51,390 --> 00:15:52,120
What else

296
00:15:52,120 --> 00:15:53,720
does he like to do?

297
00:15:54,720 --> 00:15:55,910
What does he like to do?

298
00:15:55,910 --> 00:15:56,440
Yeah.

299
00:15:58,120 --> 00:15:59,840
He likes me to clean his ears for him.

300
00:15:59,840 --> 00:16:00,770
Does this count?

301
00:16:00,910 --> 00:16:02,510
You know how to do ear cleaning?

302
00:16:02,510 --> 00:16:03,000
Yes.

303
00:16:03,440 --> 00:16:04,360
Xie.

304
00:16:04,360 --> 00:16:06,030
Could you teach me sometime?

305
00:16:06,030 --> 00:16:07,000
Of course.

306
00:16:07,630 --> 00:16:08,630
But

307
00:16:08,630 --> 00:16:11,030
you have to wait
until you enter the palace.

308
00:16:11,390 --> 00:16:12,870
Thank you, Xie.

309
00:16:14,390 --> 00:16:16,600
When the marriage alliance
was first proposed,

310
00:16:16,600 --> 00:16:18,530
all the officials were against it.

311
00:16:19,150 --> 00:16:20,440
Only I supported it.

312
00:16:21,000 --> 00:16:22,240
Now it seems

313
00:16:22,720 --> 00:16:24,080
it was the right choice.

314
00:16:29,080 --> 00:16:30,240
This hairpin

315
00:16:30,320 --> 00:16:32,440
was left to me by my late mother.

316
00:16:33,360 --> 00:16:34,620
I want to give it to you.

317
00:16:35,360 --> 00:16:36,200
Xie.

318
00:16:36,200 --> 00:16:37,750
It's such a precious gift.

319
00:16:37,750 --> 00:16:39,840
This is my love for you and Liu Chu.

320
00:16:40,150 --> 00:16:41,390
You can't refuse it.

321
00:16:44,550 --> 00:16:45,550
Thank you, Xie.

322
00:16:48,670 --> 00:16:49,790
Liu Chu and I

323
00:16:50,030 --> 00:16:51,440
will be happy.

324
00:17:02,600 --> 00:17:03,240
My Lord.

325
00:17:12,069 --> 00:17:13,310
This tea doesn't seem

326
00:17:14,480 --> 00:17:16,480
as fragrant as usual today.

327
00:17:18,160 --> 00:17:20,000
It was made just the way

328
00:17:20,000 --> 00:17:21,349
you always prefer.

329
00:17:24,000 --> 00:17:24,550
My Lord.

330
00:17:25,069 --> 00:17:26,200
Black moves first, white follows—

331
00:17:26,200 --> 00:17:27,960
you've turned the tables.

332
00:17:30,720 --> 00:17:31,960
There is no right or wrong,

333
00:17:31,960 --> 00:17:33,720
no winning or losing.

334
00:17:34,240 --> 00:17:35,110
Take it.

335
00:17:36,590 --> 00:17:38,960
It's just a game of chess.

336
00:17:39,680 --> 00:17:40,240
My Lord.

337
00:17:41,240 --> 00:17:43,370
I didn't expect Xiao Chi and the others

338
00:17:43,440 --> 00:17:45,700
to survive resolve the plague this time.

339
00:17:46,200 --> 00:17:47,550
Fate is decided

340
00:17:47,550 --> 00:17:48,640
by heaven.

341
00:17:49,680 --> 00:17:51,240
Those meant to live die,

342
00:17:51,830 --> 00:17:53,760
and those who should die are alive.

343
00:17:54,240 --> 00:17:55,500
You're right, My Lord.

344
00:17:56,110 --> 00:17:57,590
So,

345
00:17:57,590 --> 00:17:59,450
what happened in Huangpi Village

346
00:17:59,590 --> 00:18:00,830
is just over?

347
00:18:04,240 --> 00:18:06,400
Do you really believe

348
00:18:06,790 --> 00:18:08,520
they can cure all the patients?

349
00:18:08,640 --> 00:18:10,030
Who knows?

350
00:18:10,350 --> 00:18:11,240
Besides,

351
00:18:11,240 --> 00:18:12,350
even if they can be cured,

352
00:18:12,350 --> 00:18:13,960
who can guarantee

353
00:18:14,400 --> 00:18:16,310
it won't break out again?

354
00:18:18,240 --> 00:18:19,680
You mean...

355
00:18:21,350 --> 00:18:22,070
My Lord.

356
00:18:22,400 --> 00:18:23,830
You are the Grand Secretary now.

357
00:18:23,830 --> 00:18:24,880
In some matters,

358
00:18:24,880 --> 00:18:26,010
we cannot hesitate.

359
00:18:26,830 --> 00:18:28,590
We can't allow even the slightest chance

360
00:18:28,590 --> 00:18:32,160
of this plague returning.

361
00:18:36,350 --> 00:18:39,000
No wonder
you've been with me for so many years.

362
00:18:40,200 --> 00:18:41,240
That's exactly

363
00:18:41,510 --> 00:18:43,200
what I was thinking.

364
00:18:45,720 --> 00:18:47,720
The tragedy of eight years ago

365
00:18:48,200 --> 00:18:50,590
is chilling to think about.

366
00:18:51,200 --> 00:18:52,960
Send someone to deal with it—

367
00:18:54,160 --> 00:18:55,110
swiftly,

368
00:18:55,590 --> 00:18:57,110
and without causing any pain.

369
00:18:57,110 --> 00:18:57,790
Yes.

370
00:18:58,830 --> 00:18:59,720
Then...

371
00:19:00,160 --> 00:19:02,090
what about Xiao Chi and the others?

372
00:19:02,200 --> 00:19:05,510
It won't be that easy for him

373
00:19:06,270 --> 00:19:07,830
to report to His Majesty.

374
00:19:07,830 --> 00:19:08,590
Don't worry.

375
00:19:09,350 --> 00:19:10,790
I know what to do.

376
00:19:19,310 --> 00:19:20,960
Only now does this tea

377
00:19:21,440 --> 00:19:23,350
begin to have any fragrance.

378
00:19:31,400 --> 00:19:32,400
Please enjoy.

379
00:19:32,550 --> 00:19:33,720
I'll go take a look around.

380
00:19:33,720 --> 00:19:33,960
Here.

381
00:19:33,960 --> 00:19:34,560
Thank you.

382
00:19:36,830 --> 00:19:37,790
What do you think, Zheng?

383
00:19:37,790 --> 00:19:39,990
Isn't Jinglan's scenery magnificent?

384
00:19:40,590 --> 00:19:43,160
The beauty of the land
is truly awe-inspiring.

385
00:19:43,160 --> 00:19:44,510
May the realm be at peace

386
00:19:44,920 --> 00:19:46,580
and the land remain unharmed.

387
00:19:48,000 --> 00:19:50,030
Changmo also has many beautiful sights.

388
00:19:50,030 --> 00:19:52,440
Every land has its own beauty—

389
00:19:53,550 --> 00:19:55,510
it is only war and prejudice

390
00:19:56,000 --> 00:19:57,440
that blind people to it.

391
00:19:58,270 --> 00:19:59,440
Physician Han,

392
00:19:59,440 --> 00:20:01,030
that was very profound.

393
00:20:03,030 --> 00:20:03,830
I believe that

394
00:20:04,110 --> 00:20:05,000
in Changmo,

395
00:20:05,270 --> 00:20:07,000
there are also people of simple hearts,

396
00:20:07,000 --> 00:20:08,590
longing for peace and stability

397
00:20:08,590 --> 00:20:09,750
just as we are.

398
00:20:12,550 --> 00:20:14,750
May the world be at peace,

399
00:20:14,750 --> 00:20:16,280
and may there be no more war.

400
00:20:16,480 --> 00:20:17,080
Well said.

401
00:20:17,550 --> 00:20:19,070
To a world without war—

402
00:20:19,070 --> 00:20:19,530
cheers.

403
00:20:21,750 --> 00:20:22,720
Then...

404
00:20:23,000 --> 00:20:24,440
to a world without war—

405
00:20:24,680 --> 00:20:25,350
cheers.

406
00:20:27,070 --> 00:20:28,530
You'd better not drink it.

407
00:20:35,440 --> 00:20:37,350
You have all had a hard journey.

408
00:20:37,550 --> 00:20:40,200
But after spending so long
in Huangpi Village,

409
00:20:40,200 --> 00:20:40,880
there may

410
00:20:41,030 --> 00:20:43,590
still be toxins left in your bodies.

411
00:20:43,960 --> 00:20:45,680
If those were brought back to the capital,

412
00:20:45,680 --> 00:20:47,680
the consequences would be serious.

413
00:20:48,240 --> 00:20:49,030
Lord Zhang.

414
00:20:49,400 --> 00:20:52,000
Everyone in Huangpi Village
has already been cured,

415
00:20:52,000 --> 00:20:54,000
and there has been no relapse for so long.

416
00:20:54,000 --> 00:20:56,160
On what grounds do you claim
there are still toxins left?

417
00:20:56,160 --> 00:20:57,000
Lord Zhang.

418
00:20:57,310 --> 00:20:58,830
His Majesty said he would

419
00:20:58,830 --> 00:21:01,030
personally reward General Xiao.

420
00:21:01,440 --> 00:21:02,920
This can't be delayed.

421
00:21:03,070 --> 00:21:04,160
Lord Fei.

422
00:21:04,790 --> 00:21:05,920
I am only thinking

423
00:21:05,920 --> 00:21:08,350
of the safety
of the people in the capital.

424
00:21:08,750 --> 00:21:10,400
Now everyone in the capital

425
00:21:10,400 --> 00:21:12,640
already knows that
General Xiao has earned merit,

426
00:21:12,640 --> 00:21:13,720
so there is no need

427
00:21:13,880 --> 00:21:15,550
to rush the reward.

428
00:21:15,720 --> 00:21:16,510
I think

429
00:21:16,510 --> 00:21:18,680
it would be better for you

430
00:21:19,240 --> 00:21:21,350
to wait a few more days

431
00:21:21,550 --> 00:21:23,160
and enter the palace

432
00:21:23,350 --> 00:21:24,920
once you're cleared.

433
00:21:26,030 --> 00:21:27,630
I am doing this for the safety

434
00:21:27,640 --> 00:21:31,070
of His Majesty
and the people in the capital.

435
00:21:31,880 --> 00:21:32,920
I advise that

436
00:21:33,240 --> 00:21:34,680
you return to the residence

437
00:21:34,680 --> 00:21:37,340
and remain under observation
for several days.

438
00:21:41,550 --> 00:21:42,590
In that case,

439
00:21:42,750 --> 00:21:44,310
we will return to our residence and wait.

440
00:21:44,310 --> 00:21:46,400
Lord Zhang, please inform His Majesty

441
00:21:46,400 --> 00:21:49,060
that we are ready
to enter the palace at any time.

442
00:21:50,110 --> 00:21:51,310
Don't worry.

443
00:21:51,550 --> 00:21:53,510
I will pass it on.

444
00:21:54,920 --> 00:21:56,160
Open the city gate.

445
00:21:57,160 --> 00:22:00,880
Escort General Xiao and Physician Han
back to the residence.

446
00:22:02,720 --> 00:22:04,110
General Xiao.

447
00:22:04,550 --> 00:22:05,920
Please.

448
00:22:25,000 --> 00:22:26,200
What does this mean?

449
00:22:26,480 --> 00:22:28,680
Are they putting us under house arrest?

450
00:22:30,440 --> 00:22:31,900
Even if it is house arrest,

451
00:22:32,110 --> 00:22:33,840
why keep the two of us
together?

452
00:22:37,160 --> 00:22:38,680
We should take things as they come.

453
00:22:38,680 --> 00:22:40,410
It's better than going to jail.

454
00:22:40,590 --> 00:22:42,000
Why should we be imprisoned?

455
00:22:42,000 --> 00:22:43,110
We're there to save people,

456
00:22:43,110 --> 00:22:44,310
not to kill anyone.

457
00:22:45,830 --> 00:22:46,960
I don't understand.

458
00:22:47,030 --> 00:22:48,510
He was the one who sent us there,

459
00:22:48,510 --> 00:22:50,510
and also the one
who sent people to bring us back.

460
00:22:50,510 --> 00:22:52,110
Now that we're back,

461
00:22:52,240 --> 00:22:54,550
he still wants to detain us
under house arrest?

462
00:22:54,550 --> 00:22:56,750
How many Emperors are there in Jinglan?

463
00:22:57,830 --> 00:22:58,690
Physician Han.

464
00:22:58,920 --> 00:22:59,920
Watch your mouth.

465
00:23:12,680 --> 00:23:15,590
How long will Xiao Chi and the others
be under house arrest?

466
00:23:15,590 --> 00:23:16,440
A month.

467
00:23:17,880 --> 00:23:18,790
Was the outbreak in Huangpi Village

468
00:23:18,790 --> 00:23:20,160
really cured by them?

469
00:23:20,590 --> 00:23:21,550
Of course.

470
00:23:24,720 --> 00:23:26,110
Do you know something?

471
00:23:26,830 --> 00:23:27,880
How is that possible?

472
00:23:27,880 --> 00:23:29,200
I serve the princess in the residence

473
00:23:29,200 --> 00:23:30,070
every day.

474
00:23:30,070 --> 00:23:31,530
How would I know anything?

475
00:23:33,270 --> 00:23:34,880
The plague in Huangpi Village

476
00:23:34,880 --> 00:23:36,160
came unexpectedly,

477
00:23:36,400 --> 00:23:38,400
but fortunately it was
brought under control in time.

478
00:23:38,400 --> 00:23:39,590
The Imperial Medical Academy

479
00:23:39,590 --> 00:23:41,590
is now investigating its source.

480
00:23:42,480 --> 00:23:44,010
Investigating its source?

481
00:23:45,440 --> 00:23:47,700
Are you truly uninvolved in this matter?

482
00:23:48,200 --> 00:23:49,400
I know nothing.

483
00:23:50,440 --> 00:23:51,680
Before you came here,

484
00:23:51,880 --> 00:23:53,000
you told me

485
00:23:53,070 --> 00:23:55,350
your only duty was to protect the princess

486
00:23:55,350 --> 00:23:57,200
and ensure the marriage alliance.

487
00:23:57,200 --> 00:23:58,800
If you have any other orders,

488
00:23:58,830 --> 00:24:00,090
you should tell me now.

489
00:24:00,510 --> 00:24:02,000
If anything goes wrong,

490
00:24:02,350 --> 00:24:04,010
I won't be able to protect you.

491
00:24:04,200 --> 00:24:05,550
I know what to do.

492
00:24:07,350 --> 00:24:07,950
By the way,

493
00:24:08,310 --> 00:24:09,960
what kind of person is Liu Xie?

494
00:24:09,960 --> 00:24:12,090
Why are you suddenly asking about her?

495
00:24:12,550 --> 00:24:14,750
She came to see the princess a while ago.

496
00:24:16,720 --> 00:24:17,550
She

497
00:24:18,350 --> 00:24:19,680
controls the treasury,

498
00:24:19,790 --> 00:24:21,190
excels in state affairs,

499
00:24:21,400 --> 00:24:22,830
understands people well,

500
00:24:22,830 --> 00:24:24,490
and sees through everything.

501
00:24:24,510 --> 00:24:25,400
What about

502
00:24:25,550 --> 00:24:26,680
her relationship with Liu Chu?

503
00:24:26,680 --> 00:24:27,830
They are siblings,

504
00:24:27,830 --> 00:24:29,490
and they are extremely close.

505
00:24:29,640 --> 00:24:31,750
Will she interfere with the marriage...

506
00:24:31,750 --> 00:24:32,590
No.

507
00:24:33,960 --> 00:24:34,720
The alliance

508
00:24:35,000 --> 00:24:36,330
concerns both nations.

509
00:24:36,350 --> 00:24:38,310
It is not for her to decide.

510
00:24:38,830 --> 00:24:39,590
Moreover,

511
00:24:39,790 --> 00:24:41,920
His Majesty is devoted to the princess

512
00:24:42,070 --> 00:24:46,130
and has already ordered the Ministry of Rites
to hurry the arrangements.

513
00:24:51,830 --> 00:24:53,160
Lord Fei.

514
00:24:54,350 --> 00:24:55,110
Princess.

515
00:24:59,400 --> 00:25:00,160
Princess.

516
00:25:00,400 --> 00:25:01,440
Why are you awake?

517
00:25:01,750 --> 00:25:02,920
It's already late in the morning—

518
00:25:02,920 --> 00:25:04,270
I can't sleep all day.

519
00:25:05,350 --> 00:25:06,750
Since Lord Fei is here,

520
00:25:06,790 --> 00:25:08,790
let's go see Physician Han.

521
00:25:09,070 --> 00:25:11,330
I haven't seen them since they returned.

522
00:25:12,400 --> 00:25:14,590
I came here today to remind you

523
00:25:14,790 --> 00:25:16,850
to stay away from the east courtyard.

524
00:25:17,000 --> 00:25:19,160
Physician Han and General Xiao

525
00:25:19,160 --> 00:25:21,000
are being quarantined there now.

526
00:25:21,000 --> 00:25:22,110
Why?

527
00:25:22,790 --> 00:25:24,750
The outbreak
in Huangpi Village was severe.

528
00:25:24,750 --> 00:25:25,720
His Majesty

529
00:25:25,720 --> 00:25:27,400
was worried about your health,

530
00:25:27,400 --> 00:25:29,200
so he had no choice but to do this.

531
00:25:31,920 --> 00:25:34,580
I didn't expect
His Majesty to be so thoughtful.

532
00:25:35,680 --> 00:25:36,200
Well,

533
00:25:36,270 --> 00:25:38,470
they must be in need of food and clothes.

534
00:25:38,590 --> 00:25:39,270
Jin Xi.

535
00:25:39,310 --> 00:25:41,240
send them my dried meat

536
00:25:41,240 --> 00:25:42,400
and pastries.

537
00:25:46,720 --> 00:25:47,400
Okay.

538
00:25:55,400 --> 00:25:56,550
This is all the food

539
00:25:56,550 --> 00:25:58,110
we have for now.

540
00:25:58,880 --> 00:26:01,240
Looks like
we'll be stuck here for some time.

541
00:26:01,240 --> 00:26:02,000
Why?

542
00:26:02,030 --> 00:26:03,090
I'm not a prisoner.

543
00:26:16,510 --> 00:26:17,350
Open the door!

544
00:26:17,350 --> 00:26:18,310
Is anyone there?

545
00:26:19,920 --> 00:26:20,830
Is anyone outside?

546
00:26:20,830 --> 00:26:21,790
Open the door!

547
00:26:22,070 --> 00:26:22,880
Open the door!

548
00:26:22,880 --> 00:26:24,830
Let us out!

549
00:26:29,920 --> 00:26:30,440
Jin Xi.

550
00:26:31,480 --> 00:26:32,310
Tell me.

551
00:26:32,350 --> 00:26:34,240
Physician Han and General Xiao

552
00:26:34,240 --> 00:26:35,880
have gone through so much together,

553
00:26:35,880 --> 00:26:37,070
and now they're stuck

554
00:26:37,070 --> 00:26:38,270
in the same yard.

555
00:26:38,920 --> 00:26:41,590
Will they...

556
00:26:43,270 --> 00:26:45,000
Haven't you ever wondered

557
00:26:45,200 --> 00:26:47,310
what it would be like

558
00:26:47,480 --> 00:26:48,940
to be with the one you love?

559
00:26:49,640 --> 00:26:50,270
I...

560
00:26:50,400 --> 00:26:51,440
I haven't.

561
00:26:52,720 --> 00:26:53,960
Really?

562
00:26:56,030 --> 00:26:57,790
You always tease me.

563
00:26:58,480 --> 00:26:59,350
What about you?

564
00:26:59,750 --> 00:27:01,550
Don't you have someone you like?

565
00:27:02,720 --> 00:27:05,200
I think you and Lord Fei

566
00:27:05,440 --> 00:27:06,970
suit each other quite well.

567
00:27:08,240 --> 00:27:09,400
He will

568
00:27:09,400 --> 00:27:11,240
be in charge of your marriage ceremony,

569
00:27:11,240 --> 00:27:12,920
and I serve by your side,

570
00:27:12,920 --> 00:27:13,750
so it's natural that

571
00:27:13,750 --> 00:27:14,950
we have more contact.

572
00:27:15,240 --> 00:27:15,920
Oh.

573
00:27:16,110 --> 00:27:17,270
I see.

574
00:27:19,680 --> 00:27:21,830
You're often with Lord Fei—

575
00:27:22,030 --> 00:27:23,720
has he ever mentioned

576
00:27:23,790 --> 00:27:25,350
General Xiao's siblings?

577
00:27:26,720 --> 00:27:28,000
It seems

578
00:27:28,240 --> 00:27:29,590
he has an elder brother.

579
00:27:30,310 --> 00:27:31,480
What's his name?

580
00:27:32,240 --> 00:27:33,720
I don't know.

581
00:27:34,240 --> 00:27:35,310
But

582
00:27:35,310 --> 00:27:37,590
he came here a few days ago.

583
00:27:41,720 --> 00:27:44,480
So he is General Xiao's brother.

584
00:27:46,200 --> 00:27:48,680
I never thought there could be a man

585
00:27:48,680 --> 00:27:51,080
who is both so childish
and so interesting.

586
00:28:00,240 --> 00:28:03,770
Her Highness's martial skills are truly
no less than any man's.

587
00:28:04,000 --> 00:28:04,920
Her presence

588
00:28:05,440 --> 00:28:07,400
is even more imposing than General Xiao's.

589
00:28:07,400 --> 00:28:08,240
Of course.

590
00:28:08,310 --> 00:28:10,400
Her Highness is truly gifted in
both civil and military arts.

591
00:28:10,400 --> 00:28:11,920
Had she been a man,

592
00:28:12,030 --> 00:28:13,680
she would have ruled with wisdom

593
00:28:13,680 --> 00:28:15,140
and conquered with force.

594
00:28:16,550 --> 00:28:17,750
Don't talk nonsense.

595
00:28:17,750 --> 00:28:18,550
Are you crazy?

596
00:28:23,240 --> 00:28:25,440
His Majesty has arrived!

597
00:28:25,440 --> 00:28:26,200
Xie.

598
00:28:28,350 --> 00:28:29,810
Greetings, Your Majesty.

599
00:28:30,070 --> 00:28:31,240
Get up.

600
00:28:31,350 --> 00:28:32,750
Thank you, Your Majesty.

601
00:28:32,960 --> 00:28:34,960
What brings you here all of a sudden?

602
00:28:34,960 --> 00:28:37,070
Your sword skills have improved.

603
00:28:37,200 --> 00:28:38,660
You came just to praise me?

604
00:28:39,200 --> 00:28:39,720
Yes.

605
00:28:39,960 --> 00:28:41,690
I came specifically to see you.

606
00:28:41,880 --> 00:28:43,000
Just to see me?

607
00:28:43,270 --> 00:28:44,870
Nothing else you want to say?

608
00:28:46,480 --> 00:28:48,210
There is something, actually.

609
00:28:48,750 --> 00:28:49,720
I want

610
00:28:50,110 --> 00:28:53,480
to discuss the timing

611
00:28:53,880 --> 00:28:54,830
of the marriage alliance

612
00:28:54,830 --> 00:28:56,830
with the Changmo princess with you.

613
00:28:58,790 --> 00:29:00,790
She's been in Jinglan for some time.

614
00:29:01,000 --> 00:29:03,460
You've kept her
in the General's residence—

615
00:29:03,550 --> 00:29:05,030
why the sudden thought

616
00:29:05,400 --> 00:29:07,200
of bringing her into the palace?

617
00:29:09,790 --> 00:29:12,480
The alliance is a matter of state.

618
00:29:12,750 --> 00:29:13,960
It shouldn't

619
00:29:13,960 --> 00:29:15,400
be delayed any further.

620
00:29:15,480 --> 00:29:16,480
So,

621
00:29:16,680 --> 00:29:18,110
if we complete the ceremony soon

622
00:29:18,110 --> 00:29:19,480
and restore relations
between the two nations,

623
00:29:19,480 --> 00:29:21,240
the people can live

624
00:29:21,240 --> 00:29:22,270
in lasting peace,

625
00:29:22,510 --> 00:29:23,160
right?

626
00:29:27,550 --> 00:29:28,790
I heard

627
00:29:29,310 --> 00:29:31,510
the Princess of Changmo is a beauty.

628
00:29:35,880 --> 00:29:37,160
I don't know.

629
00:29:37,350 --> 00:29:38,270
Really?

630
00:29:38,270 --> 00:29:39,270
Really.

631
00:29:41,960 --> 00:29:43,680
When is the ceremony set for?

632
00:29:44,440 --> 00:29:46,000
It seems

633
00:29:46,350 --> 00:29:48,030
to be the tenth day of next month.

634
00:29:48,030 --> 00:29:49,160
It's a good day.

635
00:29:49,830 --> 00:29:51,310
You think it's a good day?

636
00:29:51,310 --> 00:29:52,270
Of course.

637
00:29:52,640 --> 00:29:53,680
My closest brother

638
00:29:53,680 --> 00:29:55,410
is marrying the woman he loves—

639
00:29:55,480 --> 00:29:56,960
it's the best day

640
00:29:56,960 --> 00:29:58,440
there could be.
